comments.body:
Good point. Since the GridTileBar can serve as a tile header or footer, maybe a separate GridTile widget would eliminate the Stack boilerplate:

```
class GridTile {
  GridTile({ Key key, this.header, this.footer, this.child }) : super(key: key);

  final Widget header;
  final Widget footer;
  final Widget child;

  ...
}

new GridTile(
  header: new GridTileBar(
    title: new Text('the footer appears on the bottom of the tile')
  ),
  child: new AssetImage(
     ...
  )
)
```

